Fountainhead Property Trust (FPT)  agreed
to buy the remaining 25 percent it doesn’t already own in
Centurion Mall for 751.5 million rand from  Hyprop Investments
Ltd. (HYP) ’s Attfund Retail Ltd.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
